data.description: Welcome to your new home in the vibrant heart of Houston's East End! This stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom property, meticulously rebuilt in 2021, offers modern comfort and timeless charm. With updated plumbing, electrical, roof, and HVAC systems, this home ensures peace of mind for years to come. The inviting open-concept floor plan boasts a chef's dream kitchen, complete with a deluxe cooktop, double ovens, and ample countertop space. Step outside to your private oasis, featuring a cozy covered area and room for a flourishing garden. Enjoy the tranquility of this neighborhood while still being conveniently close to city amenities and attractions, including Mason Park, Gus Wortham Golf Course, and Bayou Hike and Bike trails. With easy access to Metro Rail, Downtown, the Medical Center, and more, this craftsman gem offers the perfect blend of urban convenience and suburban serenity. Don't miss the opportunity to make this East End treasure your own!
